### read all users(req to protected rote)
GET http://localhost:3000/user-api/users

### read a user by id
GET http://localhost:3000/user-api/user

###create new user
POST http://localhost:3000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json 

{
    "username":"sunny",
    "password":"soujithsunny",
    "email":"sunny@gmail.com",
    "age":19
}


