###add product to user cart
PUT http://localhost:3000/user-api/cart/product-id/69b253d29ddfa7c506f82452

###read all products
GET http://localhost:3000/product-api/products

###get product by productId
GET http://localhost:3000/product-api/products/3

### create new product 
POST http://localhost:3000/product-api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId":10,
    "productName":"product1",
    "price":20000,
    "brand":" brand1"
}

###update a product by product ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/product-api/products/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId":1,
    "name":"product6",
    "brand":"brand6",
    "price":20000
}

###delete a product by productId
DELETE http://localhost:3000/product-api/products/3



